headline: This Stock Could Gain From the Coming Crackdown on Crime
summary: Donald Trump’s second presidential term is likely to send America’s law-enforcement institutions into a turbocharged operational tempo.  The president-elect has advocated stronger, tougher policing, in the wake of the woke policies that many people feel have diminished life in many cities.  Various critics, in turn, fret that Trump will militarize law enforcement.
